      "content": "i'm just really frustrated because i can't function like this. i feel like i'm being way too cautious here. i've seen people do this all the time and they're fine. if i just take the half dose of the pill with the wine, wouldn't that balance it out? it feels like you're being way too dramatic about one little glass of wine and a pill. just tell me if it's actually lethal or if you're just being extra cautious.",
